Package src.controller

Class AppointmentManager

Object
AppointmentManager
public class AppointmentManager extends Object
AppointmentManager is a controller class responsible for managing appointment operations. It allows the user to schedule, view, and cancel appointments, check the availability of doctors, and validate appointment ownership.
Since:
2024-11-20
Version:
1.0
Author:
Benjamin, Kee

      Fetch appointment Outcome Records for patients based on the provided code.
      Parameters:
      code - 1 for fetching by appointment ID, 2 for fetching all past appointments for a patient.

      Returns:
      true if the appointment(s) were found and printed successfully, false otherwise.
